Package: CrossLinkR
Type: Package
Title: R package to search for crosslinks in Hi-C data
Version: 0.1
Date: 2016-11-03
Author: David Porubsky
Maintainer: David Porubsky <d.porubsky@umcg.nl>
Description: This package implements functions to search for crosslinks phasing information from Hi-C data.
